name: Black Maternal Health Week 2022 Open Edition

metadata.name: Black Maternal Health Week 2022 Open Edition #1
metadata.description: Curio and Rock The Bells is proud to partner with Pampers as they sponsor Black Maternal Health Week, founded and led by Black Mamas Matter Alliance (BMMA), on a limited edition NFT collection. Proceeds will go back to BMMA to advance care for more Black mamas.
